WEBVTT

00:00.884 --> 00:01.884
Whoo!

00:01.885 --> 00:04.120
Extreme!
[Chuckles]

00:04.121 --> 00:06.622
Oh, you guys are probably
curious about this.

00:06.623 --> 00:07.623
It's no biggie.

00:07.624 --> 00:08.791
My car's in the shop,

00:08.792 --> 00:11.093
so I rode in on
Rosa's motorcycle.

00:11.094 --> 00:13.596
I guess you could say
I'm a gear head now.

00:13.597 --> 00:16.265
He held on to me so tight,
it was like a two-mile Heimlich.

00:16.265 --> 00:19.001
Those things have
no walls on them.

00:19.002 --> 00:21.437
Captain,
why are you sitting at my desk?

00:21.438 --> 00:24.140
Lieutenant Miller from
internal affairs is here.

00:24.141 --> 00:26.342
<i>He's taken over my office.</i>

00:26.343 --> 00:28.844
Apparently, someone has been
leaking classified information

00:28.845 --> 00:29.979
to a criminal syndicate.

00:29.980 --> 00:31.903
The entire squad is
under investigation.

00:31.909 --> 00:33.149
That's crazy.

00:33.150 --> 00:35.418
No one here's a mole.
How can you be so sure?

00:35.419 --> 00:36.485
Because I know
these guys.

00:36.486 --> 00:37.620
I know everything
about them.

00:37.621 --> 00:39.021
Well, you're
a poor police officer

00:39.022 --> 00:40.912
if you don't think people
can surprise you.

00:40.918 --> 00:42.892
Not these people.
Here, watch this.

00:42.893 --> 00:44.527
I know what everyone's
gonna do tonight.

00:44.528 --> 00:47.029
It's thursday,
so Gina's gonna leave early

00:47.030 --> 00:48.664
to rehearse with her
new dance group,

00:48.665 --> 00:49.565
dancy Reagan.

00:49.566 --> 00:50.733
There the first ladies
of movement.

00:50.734 --> 00:53.002
Amy's gonna be
going over her weekly budget.

00:53.514 --> 00:56.305
And Charles will be attending
a "pizza for one" cooking class.

00:56.306 --> 00:58.346
Tonight's menu:
Pepper-alone-I.

00:58.352 --> 01:00.474
And if I run and leap
at Terry,

01:00.480 --> 01:02.684
