rarely have my sense of humor.

01:40.605 --> 01:43.725
Wow, you are really worried
about this investigation.

01:43.731 --> 01:45.009
<i>Okay, fine.</i>

01:45.010 --> 01:46.666
I promise I will
be stone-cold serious

01:46.667 --> 01:47.611
in my interview.

01:47.612 --> 01:50.848
I'll even use
my serious face.

01:50.849 --> 01:52.750
If you're wondering
how I'm pulling this off,

01:52.751 --> 01:54.085
I'm thinking about the time
when I was eight

01:54.086 --> 01:56.087
and Don Mattingly
called me a little turd.

01:56.088 --> 01:58.156
- Was he right?
- Yes.

01:59.324 --> 02:00.367
(Jake)
Hey there.

02:00.373 --> 02:02.760
Jake Peralta.

02:02.761 --> 02:04.729
I'm sorry, handshakes
are the greatest avenues

02:04.730 --> 02:06.397
of germ transmission.

02:06.398 --> 02:08.933
I generally prefer
simple nods.

02:08.934 --> 02:10.101
Okay.

02:10.102 --> 02:13.213
Would you, uh, pass me
that hand sanitizer, please?

02:13.219 --> 02:14.972
Yeah.

02:14.973 --> 02:16.133
No, no, no!

02:16.139 --> 02:17.634
Use your elbows.

02:17.640 --> 02:19.511
<i>And keep your nostrils
closed.</i>

02:19.517 --> 02:20.911
<i>Don't breathe on it.</i>

02:20.912 --> 02:22.413
Ah!

02:22.414 --> 02:24.048
Forget it,
I'll just use a wipe.

02:24.049 --> 02:25.049
Smart.

02:25.050 --> 02:27.084
Get off, damn germs.

02:27.085 --> 02:31.422
So what information
has been leaked and by who?

02:31.423 --> 02:33.057
You don't need to know that.

02:33.058 --> 02:34.425
All you need to know

02:34.426 --> 02:35.660
is that a felony
has been committed

02:35.661 --> 02:36.861
by someone on your squad,

02:36.862 --> 02:38.496
and I'm gonna find out
who did it.

02:38.497 --> 02:41.298
Now... have you ever
taken confidential information

02:41.299 --> 02:45.036
about an ongoing investigation
out of this precinct?

02:45.037 --> 02:46.170
No.

02:46.171 --> 02:48.439
I would never do something
that stupid.

02:48.440 --> 02:50.474
I did something really stupid.
I need your help.

02:50.475 --> 02:52.176
You know how I'm kind of
a sexy bad boy

02:52.177 --> 02:53.511
who rides motorcycles
into work

02:53.512 --> 02:54.745
and is always breaking
the rules

02:54.746 --> 02:55.913
in the name of justice?

02:55.914 --> 02:57.314
I don't like where
this is going.

02:57.315 --> 02:59.450
Well, I also maybe sometimes
bring home case files

02:59.451 --> 03:00.785
to work on them after hours,

03:00.786 --> 03:02.586
and I might not be that great
about returning them.

03:02.587 --> 03:03.788
Oh, God.

03:03.789 --> 03:05.640
Are you aroused because
of what a bad boy I am?

03:05.646 --> 03:07.324
No!
No!

03:07.325 --> 03:08.426
You could be suspended
for that.

03:08.427 --> 03:09.660
He could think
you're the mole!

03:09.661 --> 03:10.661
Not so loud.

03:10.662 --> 03:13.231
Yes, Amy,
I do drink from the <i> bowl</i>

03:13.699 --> 03:14.565
definitely pulled that off.

03:14.566 --> 03:15.800
Look, I need
to get those files.

03:15.801 --> 03:17.034
Can you please
give me a ride?

03:17.035 --> 03:18.669
Fine.
I'll get my stuff,

03:18.670 --> 03:20.671
but this better not
bite me in the ass.

03:20.672 --> 03:22.239
<i>Better not bite me in the ass</i>
is the name of your sex tape.

03:22.240 --> 03:24.909
But seriously, thank you
so much for your help.

03:24.910 --> 03:26.077
Peralta.

03:26.078 --> 03:27.278
How'd it go with Miller?

03:27.279 --> 03:28.512
Fantastic, he loved me.

03:28.513 --> 03:29.980
I would give you
more details,

03:29.981 --> 03:31.482
but someone just came in

03:31.483 --> 03:34.685
to try and find
her dalmatian coat.

03:34.686 --> 03:35.953
(Wuntch)
Hello, Raymond.

03:35.954 --> 03:37.288
Madeline.

03:37.289 --> 03:40.591
I wondered why all the birds
had suddenly stopped singing.

03:40.592 --> 03:41.592
What brings you here?

03:41.593 --> 03:42.960
I heard you were
under investigation

03:42.961 --> 03:43.961
by internal affairs.

03:43.962 --> 03:45.062
Didn't wanna
miss that.

03:45.063 --> 03:46.697
So much time with your ear
to the pavement.

03:46.698 --> 03:49.567
It's a pity a truck
hasn't run over your head.

03:49.568 --> 03:50.768
Very visual.

03:50.769 --> 03:53.137
When, oh when,
will you quit police work

03:53.138 --> 03:54.731
and pursue your dream
of poetry?

03:54.737 --> 03:57.108
I'm looking
for detective Scully.

03:57.109 --> 03:58.509
You must be from I.A.B.

03:58.510 --> 04:01.446
I'm deputy chief Wuntch.
Nice to meet you.

04:01.532 --> 04:03.614
If you have a minute,
I'd love a detailed report

04:03.615 --> 04:04.715
of this investigation.

04:04.716 --> 04:06.884
I.A.B. exists outside
of department hierarchy.

04:06.885 --> 04:08.753
I don't answer to you.

04:08.754 --> 04:10.554
Detective Scully,
you're up.

04:10.555 --> 04:12.023
Oh, uh, okay...

04:12.024 --> 04:13.190
Um...

04:13.191 --> 04:14.792
No. You know what?

04:14.793 --> 04:16.192
We'll do this
over the phone.

04:16.194 --> 04:17.712
<i>(Wuntch)
Oh, Raymond.</i>

04:17.718 --> 04:19.397
An internal affairs
investigation?

04:19.398 --> 04:21.899
A drug task force
that hasn't found any drugs?

04:21.899 --> 04:23.701
This precinct's
a disaster.

04:23.702 --> 04:25.770
Maybe that's why
the birds stopped singing.

04:25.771 --> 04:27.972
Out of respect
for the death of your career.

04:27.973 --> 04:29.807
Good-bye, Raymond.

04:31.543 --> 04:32.543
Detective Diaz.

04:32.544 --> 04:34.078
Can you give me even
a shred of good news

04:34.079 --> 04:36.026
about your drug
task force?

04:36.027 --> 04:37.696
The good news is
I can be brief about it.

04:37.697 --> 04:38.970
We have nothing.

04:38.971 --> 04:42.486
Sorry. I had to talk my twins
into getting their hair done.

04:42.487 --> 04:44.922
There are some promises
involving lollipops

04:44.923 --> 04:46.741
I do not intend to keep.

04:46.747 --> 04:48.826
The task force
has made some busts.

04:48.827 --> 04:50.628
But we still haven't found
any high-level dealers

04:50.629 --> 04:52.363
or major drug stashes.

04:52.364 --> 04:53.665
But we will
soon.

04:53.671 --> 04:54.932
Is that a promise?

04:54.933 --> 04:57.868
Or just another lollipop
that no one's ever gonna lick?

04:57.869 --> 04:59.403
