at these things.

05:11.983 --> 05:14.318
So hopefully,
we'll find some giggle pig.

05:14.319 --> 05:17.772
Great. I hope there's a lot
of drug activity there.

05:17.778 --> 05:21.058
Of course, ideally,
there will be nobody

05:21.059 --> 05:22.226
