let it be there.

05:26.331 --> 05:28.199
Please, God,
let it be there.

05:28.285 --> 05:29.993
Trunk!

05:34.306 --> 05:37.375
All right, that's it.

05:37.376 --> 05:40.244
One box of files
and one box of powdered donuts

05:40.245 --> 05:41.512
from under my bed.

05:41.513 --> 05:42.680
Oh, cool.
Can I see those?

05:42.681 --> 05:43.681
Yeah, sure.

05:43.682 --> 05:44.674
Thanks.

05:44.680 --> 05:46.584
<i>Oh, no, no, no!</i>

05:46.585 --> 05:47.818
This is a new car.

05:47.819 --> 05:48.819
