06:46.411 --> 06:47.511
Mm.
Ah!

06:47.512 --> 06:49.313
Here we go.

06:51.414 --> 06:52.683
[Both gasping]

06:52.684 --> 06:55.052
Both:
Oh, my God!

06:55.053 --> 06:56.204
[All screaming]

06:56.210 --> 06:57.822
Oh, God!

06:59.418 --> 07:01.486
What is going on?

07:01.487 --> 07:03.054
Gina and I
are casual lovers.

07:03.055 --> 07:04.055
[Both groan]

07:04.056 --> 07:05.090
Ew.

07:05.091 --> 07:06.591
How long has this
been going on?

07:06.592 --> 07:08.260
<i>(Gina) We hooked up once,
last summer</i>

07:08.261 --> 07:09.428
and then the nightmare
started again

07:09.429 --> 07:10.796
about a month ago.

07:10.797 --> 07:12.964
Ever since then,
it's been orgasm-city.

07:12.965 --> 07:13.999
[Both groan]

07:14.000 --> 07:15.000
Ew!

07:15.001 --> 07:16.168
Yuck, gross.
Right, guys?

07:16.169 --> 07:17.169
Wait a minute.

07:17.170 --> 07:18.870
You lied to me?

07:18.871 --> 07:21.640
There was no "pizza for one"
cooking class tonight.

07:21.641 --> 07:23.442
You've been lying to me
for weeks!

07:23.443 --> 07:24.743
