07:24.744 --> 07:26.778
I'm teaching inner city kids
to make candles.

07:26.779 --> 07:27.846
Oh, sorry.

07:27.847 --> 07:29.648
I'm going
to a prenatal yoga class.

07:29.649 --> 07:32.484
No can do, going
to my adult tumbling class.

07:32.485 --> 07:34.186
Yes, Jake,
those were lies.

07:34.187 --> 07:36.555
