meeting.

08:56.135 --> 08:58.703
Now let's go look
for some bad kids

08:58.704 --> 09:01.339
who went to sub-par
pre-schools.

09:01.340 --> 09:03.208
That was insane.

09:03.209 --> 09:04.209
I mean, who else
is hooking up

09:04.210 --> 09:05.210
that we don't know about?

09:05.211 --> 09:06.845
Rosa and Terry?
Holt and Scully?

09:06.846 --> 09:08.613
You and Hitchcock?

09:08.614 --> 09:09.881
You need to forget
about Charles, okay?

09:09.882 --> 09:12.284
You need to get inside
and put those files back.

09:12.285 --> 09:14.968
Wait, wait, wait.
Why'd I get Hitchcock?

09:14.974 --> 09:17.053
Because you're
the girl version of him.

09:17.557 --> 09:18.490
