09:29.769 --> 09:33.638
Wuntch...
Circling me like a shark

09:33.639 --> 09:36.308
frenzied by chum.
The task force,

09:36.309 --> 09:39.311
turning into
a career-threatening quagmire.

09:39.312 --> 09:40.779
