investigation

09:40.780 --> 09:42.581
casting doubt upon
my integrity.

09:42.582 --> 09:45.081
And you ask,
"is everything okay?"

09:45.087 --> 09:48.186
I am buffeted by the winds
of my foes' enmity

09:48.187 --> 09:51.156
and cast about
by the towering waves

09:51.157 --> 09:52.991
of cruel fate.

09:52.992 --> 09:54.926
Yet I, a captain,

09:54.927 --> 09:57.385
am no longer able
to command my vessel,

09:57.391 --> 09:59.831
my precinct, from my
customary helm, my office.

09:59.832 --> 10:02.223
And you ask,
"is everything okay?"

10:02.229 --> 10:04.336
I've worked the better part
of my years on earth

10:04.337 --> 10:05.804
overcoming every prejudice

10:05.805 --> 10:07.873
and fighting
for the position I hold.

10:07.874 --> 10:11.777
And now I feel it being
ripped from my grasp.

10:11.778 --> 10:14.736
And with it...
The very essence

10:14.742 --> 10:19.282
of what defines me
as a man.

10:20.353 --> 10:25.246
And you ask,
"is everything okay?"

10:27.493 --> 10:30.251
Yeah, I hear you.

10:30.257 --> 10:32.898
My dog has taken over
my favorite chair.

10:32.899 --> 10:38.370
It's like,
how did it all slip away?

10:38.371 --> 10:41.306
Gentlemen.

10:41.307 --> 10:43.575
Damn it, Charles.
This is a crisis.

10:43.576 --> 10:45.725
Step one: Termination.

10:45.731 --> 10:47.810
You and I will never
touch again.

10:47.816 --> 10:49.854
Damn! If I'd known
it was our last time,

10:49.860 --> 10:51.516
<i>I would've moaned more.</i>

10:51.517 --> 10:53.819
Step two: Containment.

10:53.820 --> 10:56.888
We need to make sure
that no one else finds out.

10:56.889 --> 10:59.324
Yeah, Jake won't tell anyone
if I ask him not to.

